** Homework Task 1 - Cost of University
:PROPERTIES:
:HTML_CONTAINER_CLASS: badge
:END:
- Research University and the *costs* involved in /going/, /living/ and eventually /repaying/!

- Using [[https://www.ucas.com/finance/undergraduate-tuition-fees-and-student-loans][this government website]] answer the following questions:
  + What are the *two types* of /student loans/?
  + What are the *maximum amounts* for /each/?

- Using [[https://www.student-loan-calculator.co.uk/][this website]] and the notes you have from the first task, complete the following:
  + Find out /how much/ of your student loans you /will have repayed/ after *5 years*, with a /starting salary of *Â£25,000* 
  + Find out /how long/ it will take for you to *fully pay off* your /student loans/

- Using [[https://www.timeshighereducation.com/student/advice/cost-studying-university-uk#survey-answer][this news website]] complete the following:
  + List the *costs* of at least *3 essential outgoings* and *3 lifestyle outgoings* at university
  + How much will you have /left over/ a month with the *maximum* amount of *student loan*?



